summary:
Warning On August 31, 2024 the Azure Cosmos DB .NET SDK v2.x will be retired; the SDK and all applications using the SDK will continue to function;
Azure Cosmos DB will simply cease to provide further maintenance and support for this SDK.
We recommendmigrating to the latest versionof the .NET SDK v3 SDK. Note If you are using .NET Core, please see the latest version 3.x of the.NET SDK, which targets .NET Standard.

